name: Silicone Spatula - Pink
short_description: This Silicone Spatula in a vibrant pink colour is made of high-quality silicone material that is durable and long-lasting. Its large size makes it perfect for scraping and spreading batter, dough, and other food items with ease. The flexible silicone material ensures that it can easily reach every corner of your mixing bowl or pan, making it a must-have tool for any kitchen. The bright pink color adds a pop of color to your kitchen and makes it easy to spot among your other utensils. This spatula is easy to clean and dishwasher safe, making it a convenient addition to your kitchen. Get your hands on the Silicone Spatula today and make your cooking and baking experience a breeze!
